    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、遅くなってすまない\n衣装合わせのアポイントまで、ほとんど時間がないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ha‚ ha‚ sorry I'm late.\nThere's no many time left for the fitting appointment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "いえ！　{user}さんは担当アイドルが\nすっっっごい沢山いますし、少しくらい平気です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! {user}-san have so many idols\nthat you're in charge of‚ so a little bit won't be a problem.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.0796556473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "お忙しいのは分かってますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you're busy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0796556473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.6129889806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "愛は絶対に遅刻しないよな……何時に来たんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai is never late…… What time did you get here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.4129889806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "いつも三十分前でしょうか\n私、相手をお待たせするのが心苦しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's always 30 minutes before.\nI feel sorry to keep anyone waiting. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.146322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "愛の言う通り過ぎて、今は俺が心苦しいよ……\nいっそ莉央さんみたいに怒ってくれた方が気が楽だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai is so right‚ it's hurting me right now…\nIt'd be more comfortable if you just scolded me like Rio-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.146322314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8796556473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、{user}さんに\n嫌味を言った訳じゃありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ s-sorry‚ I didn't mean\nto be sarcastic to {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.0129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "sancha-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8796556473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_04_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "私、{user}さんには\n毎日が大感謝デーですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm very grateful to you ‚ {user}-san‚\nevery day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1129889806,
      "sfxList": []
    }
